sentence_jp: 電池ボックスとスイッチS1を直列に繋ぐ
sentence_en: Connect the battery box and switch S1 in series.

sentence_jp: スイッチS1とモーターを直列に繋ぐ
sentence_en: Connect the switch S1 and motor in series.

sentence_jp: スイッチS2とランプL1を並列に繋ぐ
sentence_en: Connect switch S2 and lamp L1 in parallel.

sentence_jp: スイッチS2をモーターと電池ボックスと直列に繋ぐ
sentence_en: Connect the switch S2 in series with the motor and the battery box.

sentence_jp: プロペラをモーターに載せる
sentence_en: Put a propeller on the motor.

sentence_jp: 電池を電池ボックスに入れる
sentence_en: Put two battery in the battery box.
